Cell["\<\
Resolution: use a Pauli-basis QuantumMeasurementOperator (a Pauli string \
label or one of \"X\", \"Y\", \"Z\"). The fast path applies the corresponding \
Pauli measurement directly to the tableau, keeping evaluation on the O(n^2) \
path and preserving the PauliStabilizer head:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->990060001,ExpressionUUID->"a1b1c1d1-000b-000b-000b-00000000000b"],

